dialogue.speaker: Clara
dialogue.line: Ohh hi, you must be Morty? I thought you where going to be larger, but you|are really cute.

dialogue.speaker: Marty
dialogue.line: Wow really? That is very sweet of you, I wish I could say the same...

dialogue.speaker: Marty
dialogue.line: Well I did not expect you to be this Furry, and you know, so not Birdy.

dialogue.speaker: Clara
dialogue.line: Did you even look at my Timber profile mister!?

dialogue.speaker: Marty
dialogue.line: I take this as my time to leave. Bye bye!
